Updating the Release Notes
--------------------------

1.) Create and checkout git branch for this version.
2.) Update Release_Notes.ent with the current version and past version of the software.
3.) Update the Release version in Book_Info.xml
4.) ???
5.) Update Major and Minor new features (Overview.XML). Blurb about this release in the first <para>
6.) Update any supported platforms changes (Requirements.xml)
7.) Update link to bugs in Bugs.xml. Escape your ampersands
8.) Spend some time in bugzilla finding target audiences for bug fixes and changes on a per audience basis.
9.) Update OpenNMS Release History
10.) Update document revision history
11.) If structural changes have been made, change the edition in Book_Info.xml
12.) Run a non-publish test build for sanity checks
13.) Generate and publish